# Scope of this license (本 LICENSE の適用範囲)

This MIT license applies to the **code** portions of this repository:

- `web/` — static web application (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)
- `scripts/` — audit / ETL / verification scripts (Python)
- `.github/` — GitHub workflows, templates

The **structured data** under `docs/master/`, `docs/relations/`,
`docs/civilization/*_master*.tsv` and similar files is licensed under
**CC BY-SA 4.0** — see `LICENSE-DATA`.

The **interpretation, discussion, and analytical documents** under
`docs/discussions/`, `docs/civilization/*.md`, `docs/audit/*.md` and similar
are licensed under **CC BY-SA 4.0** — see `LICENSE-INTERPRETATION`.

For the rationale of this three-layer licensing (DISC-011 採択原則 — code /
structured data / curated relational interpretation の分離)、see
`docs/discussions/DISC-011_resolution.md`.
